title: MONDAY 1/25 - Super Bowl LV is set
itunes:title: MONDAY 1/25 - Super Bowl LV is set
description:
Patrick Mahomes and the Chiefs headed back to the Super Bowl (0:10) after the win over the Bills. Hear what Mahomes had to say about the opportunity to face Tom Brady in the big game (0:41). As for Brady and the Bucs, they'll be making NFL history after beating the Packers (2:07). TB12 happy for his coach and teammates (2:37). Could Aaron Rodgers (3:20) time in Green Bay be coming to an end? He talks about his future with the Packers (3:34)
